args: Help has arrived! You guys get out\nof here and leave that thing to me.
Quit thanking me and go!\nRun as far and as fast as you can!
Gotta admit, I think I'm actually\nscared to fight this thing...
Wait, no! I DON'T gotta admit that!\nIf I let my emotions get the better of me,\nthe Rathalos will have me for lunch!
I will not abandon this hunt. I'll use\neverything I've learned and bring it down!
Now come get me, you weird Rathalos!\nHiii-ya! Take that!
Flash bombs don't work on it... \nHow do I fight something that\ndoesn't even have a weakness?
Guess I'll just do it the old-fashioned way:\nStick to the fundamentals, maintain a safe\ndistance, and go at it with all I got!
Don't get greedy now, Sarisse. Stay calm.\nWatch for an opening. It's probably gonna\ncome at you just like the other one did...
Yesss! I'm starting to learn its movements!\n...Hey, that's actually sorta rad.
Those flashy attacks threw me for a loop\nat first, but now that I take a calmer look,\nit's clear this is still just a Rathalos.
Bigger, sure—and the color is still\npretty weird—but it acts the same\nas any other.
Still, those claws definitely have\na little extra oomph to 'em.
But it uses them in the same ol' way,\nso if I stay calm, I should be okay.
It worked! Just gotta keep this up and...\nUh oh. I think my power phial just ran out.
Oh jeez, I know what that is!\nI have to get out of heeeeere!
Whew! Okay, calm down, girl.\nGet your crap together already.
My power phial may have run out,\nbut I still have plenty of materials.
Just gotta whip up a new power phial,\nset it, aaaaand... Hey-o!
Watch its movements! Find a weak point!\nIf you need something specific, improvise!
Wait, no. I'm gonna stand my ground,\nstudy it, and find a way to survive.
Okay, it's gathering its breath now...\nSo if I take advantage of that and use\nthe tip of its nose... HAAAAAAAH!
I did it! I jumped right onto it!
Ha ha! You're not the only one\nwho can fly, you dumb monster!
Now I can hit it anywhere I want!\nHead! Wings! Uh...whatever that thing is!\nHah! Hoo! Haaaaaaah! Yeaaaaaah!
By the goddess! She drove that\nblack dragon from our midst!
You saved our village! Please, you must\ncome to a feast tonight in your honor!
Aw, that's super sweet of you,\nbut I can't accept a reward yet.
Yeah, but I'm not a hero—I'm a hunter!\nAnd saving your village is just one stop\non a very long quest for me.
A hunter only gets paid when the hunt\nis over, and my prey is still out there.
Hey, look at all those animals running.\nThat dark Rathalos must be after 'em!
I may not have taken you down this time,\nbut I'm only gonna get stronger.
And when I catch you, I'm gonna\nfinish this hunt once and for all!
And so, Sarisse continues to pursue her prey—\nalong with her dream of becoming a G-rank hunter!
